r und mehr als ein Organisationsproblem thematisiert - und welches umfassende Politisierungs- und Demokratiedefizit daraus resultiert.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aEducation, HigherxAdministration. 0aEducation, HigherxPolitical aspectszGermany. 0aEducation, HigherxPolitical aspects. 0aEducation, HigherzGermanyxAdministration. 0aEducational changezGermany. 0aOrganizational changezGermany. 4aBildung. 4aBildungsforschung. 4aHochschulpolitik. 4aOrganisationssoziologie. 4aSoziologie. 4aUniversität. 4aWissenschaft. 4aWissenschaftspolitik. 4aWissenschaftssoziologie. 4aWissensgesellschaft. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aEducation.  aEducational Research.  aSociology of Organizations.  aSociology of Science.  aSociology.  aUniversity.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2000-2009z9783110463415oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Sozialw. 2000-2009z9783110463392oZDB-23-TSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839406502zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839406502423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839406502/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2000d2009  aZDB-23-TSWc2000d2009